{"tid":2062541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官：保安證供誇大失實","createTime":"2020-06-13T08:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"089821577f223c8fd1922438e643e5be5adbd4e8","tid":2062541,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/ICTP4V3EVZPQVQPRMSMLCAZDFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FICTP4V3EVZPQVQPRMSMLCAZDFI%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrsemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=4ff423e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200613%2FICTP4V3EVZPQVQPRMSMLCAZDFI%2F&h=36b777b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200613/ICTP4V3EVZPQVQPRMSMLCAZDFI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官：保安證供誇大失實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BXHEAR3O6Y376C4BQOSTPKZPKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBXHEAR3O6Y376C4BQOSTPKZPKQ.jpg&h=5ebc0626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告何秀儀<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】裁判官何俊堯裁決時指，三名立法會保安的證供不可信不可靠，不予接納，更指當中報稱受襲的一級保安助理許耀德證供有誇大失實之嫌，與現場片段不符，質疑女被告何秀儀有否真的接觸許，甚至動武，認為控方未能毫無合理疑點確立案情，裁定何普通襲擊罪脫。公民黨質疑該保安或干犯偽證罪，昨去信立法會行管會，要求召開紀律聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：公僕倘公投 政府：定必追究<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女被告脫襲擊罪<br />\n<br />\n許供稱嘗試阻止何秀儀時，遭何撞致失平衡跌倒，痛到躺在地上不能站起，手肘也無法屈曲。惟何官指閉路電視顯示許和何相距甚遠，而許事後步出會議室，其左臂更可前後擺動。何官又指，片段顯示何看見許似乎想攔住她後，已急停避免撞向許，惟許繼續向前圖抱住她，何嘗試躲避不果。何秀儀最終獲判普遍襲擊不成立。<br />\n<br />\n五名公民黨議員昨去信立法會行管會，要求就保安員在法庭作不誠實證供召開紀律聆訊，。。。。。。。。。。。。。管會主席已收到議員信件，會適時跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭語霆"},{"pid":"7e2ef124581a972fc141639fc8424c5cf133b7ca","tid":2062541,"uid":77092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8327fc31ad0a93da9c647ab8a91c5f764288ae42","tid":2062541,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"唔誠實嘅保安成為最大的保安漏洞"},{"pid":"46e7730e46c075678e91dea90a6fdda98dc425e3","tid":2062541,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b66ff72c455f27f1a3f64aa4d70c14543f9d27","tid":2062541,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70987d797cfd3fca7227fd9322182d7f6eeb3a6f","tid":2062541,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"傻西同律司黨 對打<br />\n被人反咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbba449fdc5ffb772efa6f819bcc0ade9da1e361","tid":2062541,"uid":222238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清官, 法治最後一線生機"},{"pid":"00e78d8f5ea7ae61909c5be7e759461ba7c38edf","tid":2062541,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e2ef124581a972fc141639fc8424c5cf133b7ca","tid":2062541,"uid":77092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"港共班人好多時都犯左誹謗罪，差在當事人肯唔肯告佢地"},{"pid":"699b2c351de13b94576707eed7e6977c7476e9c6","tid":2062541,"uid":155253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"一定要追擊釘死個石q<br />\n老屈得咁爽"},{"pid":"61f91382485ba3960df50427d105452f47150f89","tid":2062541,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"佢揸住把圓月灣刀，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追，一路追..."},{"pid":"bf9b5f1a26ed831685a41b0a6a921f784acbabe6","